@Notification.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5210
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT_FROM_AUTH_LOGIN

### Get my notifications (calling user)
GET {{Notification.API_HostAddress}}/api/notifications/my?skip=0&take=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get only unread notifications
GET {{Notification.API_HostAddress}}/api/notifications/my?isRead=false
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get unread count
GET {{Notification.API_HostAddress}}/api/notifications/my/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Mark a single notification as read
POST {{Notification.API_HostAddress}}/api/notifications/1/read
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Mark all my notifications as read
POST {{Notification.API_HostAddress}}/api/notifications/my/mark-all-read
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List all notifications (Admin / ClinicalTrialManager only)
GET {{Notification.API_HostAddress}}/api/notifications?skip=0&take=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Filter all notifications by type
GET {{Notification.API_HostAddress}}/api/notifications?type=AdverseEventAlert
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get single notification by id
GET {{Notification.API_HostAddress}}/api/notifications/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Send a notification (Admin / ClinicalTrialManager)
POST {{Notification.API_HostAddress}}/api/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipientUserId": 3,
  "title": "Adverse Event Requires Review",
  "message": "A new Severe adverse event has been reported for Protocol LT-001. Immediate review required.",
  "type": "AdverseEventAlert",
  "relatedEntityType": "AdverseEvent",
  "relatedEntityId": 1
}

### Send a visit reminder
POST {{Notification.API_HostAddress}}/api/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipientUserId": 5,
  "title": "Upcoming Visit Reminder",
  "message": "Your scheduled visit (Baseline Assessment) is in 3 days on 15-Jun-2026.",
  "type": "VisitReminder",
  "relatedEntityType": "Visit",
  "relatedEntityId": 7
}

### Soft-delete notification (Admin only)
DELETE {{Notification.API_HostAddress}}/api/notifications/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
